title: Fidget - Concussive Thought
description:
A necrotic decent into the neuroses of the normal. Sometimes satirical, often biting; songs about a regular man&#039;s fight with reality, often amusing frustrations, and obsessive fear of clowns.

Concussive Thought is hard groove driven music. With elements of metal, alternative, and a little jazz. Fidget is heavily influenced by 
David Bowie, Rush, Metallica, The Cure, and frightening pictures of clowns... Seriously; clowns are REALLY scary... really...

We hope you like it!
